<lyrics>[V1]
 msẖ kẖạyf ʿly̱ nfsy mʿạk wlạ hạtdạry̱ wlạ hạtjml wạ̉nạ wyạk
 ạ̉ṣl ymynk dy sndạny wʿynyk dạymaⁿạ btrʿạny
 mhmạ bʿdt mạ btnsạny mhmạ ḍʿft fy ḍʿfy ạ̉lqạk
 mạ ạ̹nt ạ̉bwyạ lyh hạtjml wạ̉nạ mʿạk btṭmny wtqwl ạ̹ydy dy sẖạylạk
 mạtkẖạf ʿly̱ sẖklk wyạyạ slm ly ạldfẗ wạrtạḥ
 tḍʿf tqwy̱ ạ̹nt jwạyạ ṣwrtk qdạm ʿyny njạḥ
 mạ fy zyk yạ yswʿ qlby yḥbk yạ yswʿ
 ạ̉nạ mdywn lk yạ yswʿ</lyrics>
<title>msẖ kẖạyf</title>
</song>